{"title":"苦尽甜来——西藏民歌选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦尽甜来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——西藏民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北斗星最亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈达不要多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要一条洁白的就行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友不要太多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能结识一个解放军就好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时我的心呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会像开放的鲜花一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的星星虽多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有北斗星最亮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上的人虽稠密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有共产党和解放军最好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兔脚虽短"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹿角再长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却顶不上青天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兔脚虽短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能跑遍高山平原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏胞虽苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要在共产党领导下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能改地换天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党来了苦变甜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜马拉雅山再高也有顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澜沧江再长也有源，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏族人民的痛苦再深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党来了苦尽甘来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在共产党的领导下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏是个好地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种宝贝地下藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金银铜铁样样有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊遍山岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏是中国的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏汉如同一个爹娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在共产党的领导下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家得到解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要积极支援解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥护共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让强盗害怕地看见我们团结如钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的领土——西藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏是祖国的边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许反动分子撒谎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放后的新建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给藏族人民带来了吉祥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云霭低吻着山峦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗在山峰飘荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党和毛主席呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人间幸福的太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣的共产党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高耸入云的雪山在微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿得发茵的草坪在鼓掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小牧童在高声歌唱——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣的共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了我们解放军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年的眼泪流不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年的山歌唱不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了我们的人民解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨开乌云见青天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}